  "human_readable_summary": "AI governance event recorded for system ClaimsTriageAI-v1. System purpose: Triage inbound health insurance claims to prioritize high-urgency clinical cases for human adjuster review. Does not approve, deny, or adjust claim amounts; produces an ordered queue only.. Risk tier: high. Deployment context: Production clinical-operations environment at a regional health insurance carrier. Integrated into the claims adjuster queue; adjusters always make the final determination.. Responsible parties: Chief Data Officer (accountable), Head of Claims Operations (responsible), AI Governance Lead (consulted), Privacy Officer (informed). Applicable Annex A controls: A.6.2.3, A.6.2.8, A.3.2, A.5.4, A.6.2.4, A.6.2.6, A.7.2, A.7.5, A.5.5, A.8.3.",
